name: Etosha Robotics
product_desc:
MIRACLE NOMAD
Our flagship bipedal robot, Miracle Nomad (MN3) was born on the beautiful but unforgiving Etosha Pan. A robust and rugged robotics platform, MN3 is the first truly integrated self-sustaining, sentient, and fully International Robotic Ethics Commission (IREC) Certified robot available for export.*

DEW FARMER
Dew Farmer answers a critical need in drought stricken and resource scarce regions for clean water by harvesting pure moisture and performing complete filtration, self maintenance, and remote sensing of environmental fluctuations in both native aquifers and precipitation.*

THE HATCHERY
Producing native curiosity and self-aware AI neural networks was a breakthrough technology brought to the world by Dr. Frederick Yanko, and our patented Sakana Hatchery system builds on his discovery by utilizing animal kingdom hosts to develop optimal candidate AI. The initial process of selection begins with exceptional behaviors modeled on Phylum Chordata.*
high_concept: With Nature as our model, we build curious machines.

name: Game Farm Namibia
product_desc:
INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY
Seeking funds to purchase 1905 hectares of land to establish a pristine high-value Rare, Exotic and Endangered Game Breeding Project in Namibia
We are seeking a Partner/Investor that is willing to provide the initial Start-up Capital to enable the establishment of a pristine Exotic & Rare Game Farm in Namibia.
A single Investment Amount of US$ 550,000 is required; to purchase the land and wildlife. 

The dominant local large game species is kudu, oryx and Hartmann zebra. Springbuck and giraffe are found occasionally. Smaller game consists of warthog, duiker, steenbuck and klipspringer.

The most profitable venture in a small area as here would be to go into the breeding of high value game such as sable, roan or black-nosed impala.

Very lucrative is the breeding of the so-called small five including damara dik dik, steenbokkie, duiker and klipspringer All four species are present on the property.
 
LOCATION: Approximately 270km from Windhoek
high_concept: Invest in 1900 hectare Game Farm in Namibia

name: Natrescom Import-Export
product_desc: Export of small livestock from Namibia to KwaZulu-Nathal (SA). The company is positioned as a Black Empowerment Entity, where the Zulu natives want to do business with Zulu and not the white population where it comes to buying of live goats. The goat, which is a highly respected animal in the Zulu culture, is used for several functions within the community of about 12 million Zulu's who mainly live in KwaZulu-Nathal. The decision where to buy the goat is in the hands of the Sangoma's (medicine man), where we have close ties with. My background is a Dutch National with a wide African experience in several countries. My partner in business is a Native Zulu, in the direct blood line of Shaka Zulu. Business contains buying of livestock in Namibia, sell it in KwaZulu-Nathal. Highly liquid, highly profitable. Max capacity 1.600 goats on a weekly basis.
